name: 朱特·达雷
introduction: During high school, Jutt's drama teacher suggested that he drop out of school and move directly to Hollywood, California, to pursue a career in the entertainment industry. Not wanting to rush directly into filmmaking, but study the craft, Jutt took classes from New York University Tisch School of the Arts. Jutt then took additional time to train in all aspects of film & television production in Los Angeles, California. Where he lives today.
